Package: ggqualpal
Title: Qualitative Color Palettes and 'ggplot2' Scales Based on 'qualpalr'
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Alessandro", "Fuschi", , "alessandro.fuschi.work@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Tools to generate perceptually distinct qualitative colour
    palettes and 'ggplot2' discrete scales using the algorithm implemented in
    the 'qualpalr' package. The package provides simple wrappers for building
    named palettes, mapping categories to colours, and applying qualitative
    palettes to 'ggplot2' graphics.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Depends:
    R (>= 4.0)
Imports: 
    cli (>= 3.6.0),
    ggplot2 (>= 3.5.0),
    qualpalr (>= 1.0.1),
    scales (>= 1.4.0)
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
